data.title: Norby, the Mixed-up Robot by Isaac Asimov, Janet Asimov
data.meta_description: Jeff Wells was flunking out of the Space Academy until Norby the second-hand teaching robot tries to help but only complicates Jeff's life even more with his antics. In these first two chapters, Jeff learns about Norby's special features & unusual abilities.
